definition: to do/to grow/to write or compose/to pretend/to regard as/to feel/writings or works

sentences.english: The workbench provides access to all problem determination and support capabilities.
sentences.chinese: 工作台提供对所有问题确定和支持功能的访问。

sentences.english: A workbench is set up to assemble analog cameras in the Leica assembly room.
sentences.chinese: 在徕卡的装配车间里，安置着组装类似相机的工作台。

sentences.english: This list is initialized by the workbench selection.
sentences.chinese: 这一列表是由工作台选择初始化的。

sentences.english: Fasten the pulley and the support block to your worktable.
sentences.chinese: 拴紧对你的工作台的滑车和支承区块。

sentences.english: For remote-workbench debugging, you won't need to specify a project.
sentences.chinese: 对于远程工作台调试，您无须指定项目。

sentences.english: Look at your work desk and your room.
sentences.chinese: 看下你的工作台和你的房间。

sentences.english: Friction is an important factor influencing positioning precision of the AC servo XY worktable.
sentences.chinese: 摩擦是影响XY交流伺服工作台定位精度的重要因素。

sentences.english: Sometimes the use of electric tools produce its own table or some such hangers.
sentences.chinese: 有时也使用电动工具自行制作一些工作台或架子等。

sentences.english: By working with the laminar box you have to keep strict working protection and disinfection scheme.
sentences.chinese: 使用超净工作台时必须保持严格防护并遵守消毒规程。

sentences.english: The guide rail of working table has large span and strong anti-overturn capacity.
sentences.chinese: 工作台导轨跨距大，抗颠覆能力强。

sentences.english: More convenient for the storage of substrates.
sentences.chinese: 工作台为进出式，便于承印物的取放。

sentences.english: This functionality is currently only available for product add-ons installed in the workbench.
sentences.chinese: 目前，只有安装在工作台中的产品附件提供这个特性。

sentences.english: I sit at a table in the design studio.
sentences.chinese: 在设计室里，我是坐在工作台旁边。
设备和工作台丝杠覆盖。

sentences.english: The precision is largely increased with the orientation system on the table.
sentences.chinese: 加装工作台定位系统，可使印刷精度显著提高。

sentences.english: A 6-D macro-micro-displacement controllable precision operating stage is developed.
sentences.chinese: 研制了一种六维宏微位移可控精密工作台。
